import org.apache.spark.sql._
import org.apache.spark.sql.hive.thriftserver._
import org.apache.spark.sql.hive.HiveContext
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.{StructType,StructField,StringType,IntegerType,LongType,FloatType,TimestampType};

val hiveContext = new HiveContext(sc)

val productDF = hiveContext.read.format("com.databricks.spark.csv").option("header", "true").option("inferSchema", "true").load("/tmp/DimProduct/DimProduct.csv")
productDF.registerTempTable("DimProductDF")
productDF.show()
